\b 17. Suggested Handoff Note For Customer Teams\b0\par
\par
If you need to hand this to a customer or internal operator, use this short message:\par
\par
"First deploy the application and Azure resources. Second, complete the database initialization. Prefer management-group-based RBAC for larger estates. If the customer wants to reuse an existing SQL server, Key Vault, or worker storage account, pass the existing-resource inputs up front and confirm the private connectivity and RBAC assumptions before deployment."\par
